{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "ArroPay Disbursement API",
    "description": "Bank disbursement endpoints (INSTAPAY / PESONET) for the adminpanel Laravel API.\n\nBase URL variable: `{{base_url}}` (default: http://localhost)\n\nFlow:\n1. Get Banks — list supported banks for a channel\n2. Initiate Bank Withdraw — start withdrawal, receive transaction_id for OTP\n3. Process Bank Withdraw — confirm with OTP (by transactionId or orderNumber)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "channel",
      "value": "INSTAPAY",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "order_number",
      "value": "UPY-ORDER-0001",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "transaction_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "otp",
      "value": "654321",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Get Banks",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Banks (INSTAPAY)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"channel\": \"INSTAPAY\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/disbursement/banks",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "disbursement", "banks"]
            },
            "description": "Retrieve supported bank list for INSTAPAY channel.\n\n**Required:** `channel` (INSTAPAY or PESONET)\n\n**Success response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"channel\": \"INSTAPAY\",\n  \"banks\": [...]\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Banks (PESONET)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"channel\": \"PESONET\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/disbursement/banks",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "disbursement", "banks"]
            },
            "description": "Retrieve supported bank list for PESONET channel."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Initiate Bank Withdraw",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Initiate Bank Withdraw (INSTAPAY)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.transaction_id) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('transaction_id', json.transaction_id);",
                  "    }",
                  "    if (json.order_number) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('order_number', json.order_number);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"Juan Dela Cruz\",\n  \"phone\": \"9171234567\",\n  \"accountNumber\": \"09478813606\",\n  \"bankCode\": \"GXCHPHM2\",\n  \"channel\": \"INSTAPAY\",\n  \"amount\": 100,\n  \"orderNumber\": \"{{order_number}}\",\n  \"notifyUrl\": \"https://merchant.example.com/disbursement/notify\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/disbursement/initiatebankwithdraw",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "disbursement", "initiatebankwithdraw"]
            },
            "description": "Start a bank withdrawal and generate a transaction reference for OTP confirmation.\n\n**Required fields:**\n- fullName\n- phone (10, 12, or 13 digits)\n- accountNumber\n- bankCode\n- channel (INSTAPAY or PESONET)\n- amount (minimum 1)\n\n**Optional:**\n- orderNumber\n- notifyUrl\n\n**Success response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"status\": \"PENDING\",\n  \"message\": \"Disbursement is pending.\",\n  \"channel\": \"INSTAPAY\",\n  \"order_number\": \"UPY-ORDER-0001\",\n  \"provider_order_number\": \"...\",\n  \"transaction_id\": \"...\"\n}\n```\n\nOn success, `transaction_id` and `order_number` are saved to collection variables for the process step."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Initiate Bank Withdraw (PESONET)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"Juan Dela Cruz\",\n  \"phone\": \"9171234567\",\n  \"accountNumber\": \"09478813606\",\n  \"bankCode\": \"GXCHPHM2\",\n  \"channel\": \"PESONET\",\n  \"amount\": 100,\n  \"orderNumber\": \"{{order_number}}\",\n  \"notifyUrl\": \"https://merchant.example.com/disbursement/notify\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/disbursement/initiatebankwithdraw",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "disbursement", "initiatebankwithdraw"]
            },
            "description": "Initiate a PESONET bank withdrawal."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Process Bank Withdraw",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Process Bank Withdraw (by transactionId)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"transactionId\": \"{{transaction_id}}\",\n  \"otp\": \"{{otp}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/disbursement/processbankwithdraw",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "disbursement", "processbankwithdraw"]
            },
            "description": "Confirm an initiated withdrawal using OTP (Option A — by transactionId).\n\n**Required:**\n- otp\n- transactionId OR orderNumber\n\n**Success response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"status\": \"PROCESSING\",\n  \"message\": \"Disbursement is processing.\",\n  \"channel\": \"INSTAPAY\",\n  \"order_number\": \"UPY-ORDER-0001\",\n  \"provider_order_number\": \"...\",\n  \"transaction_id\": \"...\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Process Bank Withdraw (by orderNumber + channel)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"orderNumber\": \"{{order_number}}\",\n  \"channel\": \"{{channel}}\",\n  \"otp\": \"{{otp}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/disbursement/processbankwithdraw",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "disbursement", "processbankwithdraw"]
            },
            "description": "Confirm an initiated withdrawal using OTP (Option B — by orderNumber + channel).\n\n**Required:**\n- otp\n- orderNumber (channel recommended when using orderNumber)"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth (optional)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "ArroPay V2 Auth Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"apiSecret\": \"1234\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v2/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v2", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Optional ArroPay API v2 auth login proxy (if needed for other integrations)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
